dataLineage.statement:
Layer was downloaded as a shapefile by ITOS from HDX. It was then analyzed by ITOS for errors. Those errors were corrected and then the layer was sent back to UNOCHA as a feature class within a file geodatabase.
The following was found and fixed by ITOS: 1. Created and populated a reference name field. 2. Fixed spacing errors in numbered Admin2 names (for example, "Sanquin Dist# 1" was changed to "Sanquin Dist #1"). 3. Populated Admin0 p-code with 2-letter ISO code "LR". 4. Fixed 12 nesting errors between other Admin layers.
The following was found but not addressed in this version: 1. The presence of a slash in Admin2 name "Pleebo/Sodoken" may indicate the presence of an AltName that should be separated and placed in an AltName field.
